  "literalTranslation": {
    "wordAligned": "And -when- said Abraham, 'My Lord,- make this a city secure and provide its people from the fruits - whoever- of them- believed in Allah and the Day -the Last.' –He said.- And whoever disbelieved, then- I will grant him enjoyment a little; then I will force him to the punishment of the Fire, and wretched -is- the destination."
  },
